Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.06,0:00:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}據說人死後
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.62,0:00:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就能登入極樂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.28,0:00:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我卻不這麼認為
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}逝者的生命一定在生者的心間旅行
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.93,0:00:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}化為回憶…流淌
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如同我爸爸媽媽那般
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}寄宿在我們的心中
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.75,0:00:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.20,0:00:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這些也終將消卻
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.00,0:00:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以人們才會想留下些什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.16,0:00:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了不被忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.24,0:00:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}有照出來嗎…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.23,0:00:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}取景器一片黑的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不被忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.77,0:01:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真美的手
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.33,0:01:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.68,0:01:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 我為什麼會…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.26,0:01:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…昨天是…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.76,0:01:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天是想試試高感光膠卷
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.81,0:01:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.88,0:01:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再不起來要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.36,0:01:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.78,0:03:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去國外出差？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 不過就三個月
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.29,0:03:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去哪？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.18,0:03:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}玻利維亞
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.21,0:03:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是人手不夠
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 小海
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說姐姐該去嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你想去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能自己做飯
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.51,0:03:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且又快暑假了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.15,0:03:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一個人了別太放縱了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吃相不好！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回來的時候會去買點東西
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過七點前會回來的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了 走好哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也是 走好
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一個人生活…嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個位置不錯
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紅色的…頭髮？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.42,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}究竟是…為什麼…會這麼顯眼的？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是不是…有哪裡搞錯了？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊 地方找好了嗎？海
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天不是去找地方了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拿著那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 昨天只是去測試膠卷…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要拍電影了吧？導演
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.15,0:05:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是隨便拍拍 不知不覺的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼啊 我還想著來幫幫你呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過不過…如果哲郎同學在電影裡上鏡的話
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.49,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女生們肯定高興死了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就算啦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說回來 美櫻你才是要試試嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海 美櫻主演可以吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正值夏日 和偶像的印像錄影集很相配呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.09,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又不用花多少錢也不用劇本的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會…會被盯著看
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會被亂想
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 男生的慾望一覽無遺
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.85,0:05:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實想做些什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼是指？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然還太不清楚
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是想
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊 畢竟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們可是高中生啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又是夏天
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.48,0:06:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 感覺是得做些什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 我還在想你在拍什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來喜歡那種類型的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}攝影機還在拍哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…那個 不是這樣…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.17,0:06:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才那人確實和柑菜是正相反的類型呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔 有很多
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以說是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說了有很多含義嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.85,0:06:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.71,0:06:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說來你這人…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了算了 都冷靜下來 柑菜
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.58,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然 當時的我並沒有發覺
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}遲到了很抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.09,0:07:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我從今天起轉學到貴校
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫貴月一夏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}屬於我們的電視劇
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已然開始
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}鏡頭的畫面正流轉著
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在以前的學校有參加什麼社團活動麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這時候轉學很少見呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}頭髮的顏色好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有在和誰交往嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快散開
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.71,0:07:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一群餓狼
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了啊 山乃
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正是同學
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們啊 如果不老實點…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可會倒大霉哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天中午吃什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了對了 昨天的電視啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫山乃檸檬
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.87,0:07:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…我是貴月一夏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦…有什麼奇怪的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們看來能成為好朋友呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}山乃同學
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫檸檬就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那檸檬 能問你一件事嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼啊？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼你穿著不一樣的校服呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}秘密
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可告人的秘密
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說回來 你這飲食真是不均衡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 哪裡不對了？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}碳水化合物和水份
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是挺OK的組合嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼地方奇怪了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這個人很奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哪裡奇怪 怎麼奇怪了？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}名字叫貴月一夏
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天正式轉入三年級A班
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身高160cm
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.56,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}體重41kg
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.50,0:08:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}三圍從上到下是 92-58-88
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}鞋碼是…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎樣查到的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個嘛…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.34,0:09:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老師 轉校過來的那位三年級學姐的個人資料…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同學你真是的 別告訴其他人哦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概就像這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不就是赤裸裸的犯罪嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.12,0:09:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.61,0:09:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客氣
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.86,0:09:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喲 吃過了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.37,0:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此 又想偷拍嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.28,0:09:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是啊 那只是偶然照到的…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.20,0:09:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你煩人！
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.15,0:09:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說真的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 打你啊 快說真話啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.93,0:09:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很痛啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.91,0:09:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}囉嗦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在吃醋呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.14,0:09:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 就這麼定了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不行啊 而且又沒有帶可愛的泳裝來
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.30,0:09:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海 我們走
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去是…去哪裡
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 我的飲食哪裡…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}午安
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思 能佔用你一點時間嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 哲郎 你想要幹嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦好啦 交給我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…沒什麼…那個…有什麼事？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…你是今天剛轉校過來的貴月一夏學姐吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.57,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是一年級的石垣哲郎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他是霧島海人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.95,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}實際上我們幾個人在一起拍著電影玩兒
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 學姐…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以的話 能出演我們的電影嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你在突然說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…如果我可以的話
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請務必讓我幫忙
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開始運轉的事物 就不能輕易停下來
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.12,0:10:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}艾拉薇莉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也要參加
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.96,0:11:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是三年級的山乃檸檬
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就在自己也全然不覺的時候……
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.20,0:11:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}三年級?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.20,0:11:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}高年級的？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.54,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}鏡頭就開始運轉了…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀…原本只是想隨便試試的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.04,0:11:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真沒想到會成功啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏學姐 太好說話了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真是太亂來了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想做就做 這是我的作風
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 心情真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這景色也真是別致
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像個老頭子似的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶吶 真的要拍嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都已經那麼和學姐說過了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.92,0:11:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.78,0:11:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會…會拍些什麼呢…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那些就交給小小隻的檸檬學姐吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢竟…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影的內容就交給我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正好有本為盧卡斯寫的書
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好萊塢頂級導演？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是自己要寫吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她都這麼說了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼…我也參加
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.63,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}後台工作人員的話我也能來幫下忙吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不不 美櫻還是出演吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這不行的不行的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼 有什麼不行？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.61,0:12:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.31,0:12:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影…啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.27,0:12:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}導演 能指導我的…演技嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貼身扶腰教哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是手把手啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}手取り足取り被他說成是腰 這裡取意譯
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在笑些什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.05,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.85,0:12:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個呀 這個
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個 不是吻痕嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.57,0:12:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.81,0:12:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…看到了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.66,0:12:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以說了是吻痕
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天拍攝的時候被蟲咬了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 這種事我根本不記得
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…好像默認了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道有印像了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂喂 你到底在拍點什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都說了不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}農民的地租經驗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}市民的自由言論集會…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.25,0:13:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和別國的平等條約的締結要求
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來很精神
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}根據這三點主張…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那明天的休息日 大家就碰個面
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}舉行電影開拍大會
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.39,0:13:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐她們就由我來聯繫了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.68,0:13:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼我就先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天見
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.63,0:13:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.64,0:13:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼我也…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 當心點哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別看他那樣其實是很期待的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.34,0:14:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.12,0:14:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.36,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.81,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做了什麼多餘的事嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你指什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了 契機越多越好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種從上往下看的感覺 總讓人覺得惱火
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在那飄飄然個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 電影嗎…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣應該沒什麼錯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.95,0:14:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.92,0:14:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫海人 霧島海人
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 海人同學
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 為什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 我從那邊看到你
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是在…釣魚吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 這是我的興趣
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這雖然是很好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這條河 沒有魚哦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你告訴我
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.71,0:15:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能幫上忙就好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.90,0:15:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我對這附近還不熟 真是幫我大忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.46,0:15:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…釣魚的話 再稍微走一段路就能見到一條大點的河了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那裡的話就一定能…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼我就先…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 以後還請多多關照
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.65,0:15:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}彼此彼此 請多關照
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做了件讓自己遺憾的事嗎…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是再多交流交流
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼說呢 就像是…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.90,0:16:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說白了就是
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.87,0:16:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏學姐是一個人搬來這裡的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厲害 怎麼會知道的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看你手上的行李就知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}簡單的推理而已
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後我又進一步推理了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐因為沒有住的地方 非常困擾
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又猜中了真厲害
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和要入住的地方間發生了什麼意外
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正確 正確
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實現在正流落街頭
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那種地方釣魚就是最好的證據
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又正確啦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.78,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要來…我家嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.20,0:16:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是一夏學姐願意的話
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順便一提 這裡就是我家
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 好大的房子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是去世的奶奶的房子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大的對我來說太過了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多住學姐一個根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.05,0:17:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是太棒了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.31,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且 住一起的話就能進行電影的演技指導了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.33,0:17:17.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「手取り腰取り」其實應該是「手取り足取り」 含義是即使細小的環節也能照顧到。
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這才貼身扶腰指導啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得是手把手啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是 現實嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 從什麼時候開始的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}蠻久前了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.05,0:17:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我真是很困擾呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.30,0:17:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 你指的是？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？ 就是「不來我家嗎」
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 從這裡開始的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.44,0:17:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…等一下 剛才那是我的妄想…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對 是自言自語
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且我姐姐還在家裡
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.60,0:17:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然帶女孩子回家的話 有點太唐突了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…說的也是呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉啊 這樣勉強你
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.82,0:18:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…那個…學姐要去哪呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.39,0:18:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就在這附近找一個比較方便露宿的地方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…沒辦法了！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦…七海姐
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 是柑菜醬啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.49,0:18:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是少見呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼早 在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}工作已經交班了 然後還有別的事
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.01,0:18:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別的事？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.03,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 但是它卻突然不動了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.90,0:18:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對了！柑菜醬能不能幫我一個忙呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你先在那坐一會兒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}行李的話就先…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好重
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是怎麼帶它到這裡的啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是重…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.48,0:18:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然很重但是使勁拉就可以有竅門的！
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉 總之只能住一晚哦
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有今晚…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.66,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.49,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 我是第一次進男孩子的房間
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.89,0:19:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 這…這樣啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 不能再這樣悠閑了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.36,0:19:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我待會兒給你送晚飯…哦不…還有姐姐大概七點回來…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在就先洗個澡吧 換洗的衣服在那裡面嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱…歉…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那箱子裡…裝的是什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.14,0:19:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…這個是洗髮水
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.38,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}睡衣…睡衣…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐的睡袍…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姑且算是搞定衣服了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}衣…衣服就放在洗衣機上了…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝啦
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.27,0:20:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用把門打開啦！
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}離七點還早呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天這算什麼啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.53,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和學姐相遇 決定做電影…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐不知為什麼到我的家裡來…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.87,0:20:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之我也先收拾下行李換換衣服吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.15,0:20:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 這個也得收一下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.18,0:20:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼回事 這裡被蟲子刺了一下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學 這個衣服啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.20,0:20:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學！？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學！海人同學！
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎麼了…振作一下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.35,0:21:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…細胞的代謝變得…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.46,0:21:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了 起作用了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.28,0:21:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起…對不起啊 已經沒事兒了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是幫大忙了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.67,0:21:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 柑菜醬
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.66,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼啦 不過…要出差3個月啊？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.72,0:21:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 海人就拜託柑菜你啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算去一起住也沒關係啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 那種事！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.67,0:22:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為姐姐會支持柑菜醬你啦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什…什麼意思嘛！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.74,0:22:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊呀 還裝傻
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…這個…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.00,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐的眼睛好像又有點不舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.36,0:22:19.91,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像光線太強烈了 看到了海人和一個女的抱在一起的幻覺…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.31,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那算什麼嘛 好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.63,0:22:23.60,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.87,0:22:32.82,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.87,0:22:41.39,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在 在 在 在做什麼啊！？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.10,0:22:42.76,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.98,0:22:43.92,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之你們先分開！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.90,0:22:47.32,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然這是理所當然的事 但是我卻沒有發覺
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.84,0:22:55.53,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們所知道的…我們所留下的…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.01,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想讓你知曉
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.63,0:23:34.90,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我那些…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.47,0:23:36.79,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}滿溢而出的回憶
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.30,0:23:38.32,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但它卻停不住腳步

